{"tid":1939030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際奧委會：不排除東京奧運延期舉行","createTime":"2020-03-23T02:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T03:00:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ae1db9252e3ba8949d1c2b23e09cc098fdc892","tid":1939030,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:17:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國際奧委會表示，不會考慮取消東京奧運，但不排除會延期。<br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會周日召開緊急會議，會後發聲明表示，不會考慮取消東京奧運會，但就會因應疫情制定應變計劃，又改變口風指，延期舉行是其中一個選項；國際奧委會將於未來四星期內作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會一直堅持東京奧運會如期舉行，又指主辦單位已承諾會做好防疫措施，惹來多個主要體育聯會和奧運委員會批評，認為堅持如期舉行會增加運動員受感染風險。<br />\n<br />\n早前有消息指，東京奧組委正制定延期舉行奧運方案。"},{"pid":"0b1e8c83763129c8bada27c26a84574e1523a6c1","tid":1939030,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=385339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385339&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=35135435\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385339&h=7c030f02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=385339</a>"},{"pid":"c5b63ecb9469ebc8c70b0078bb9dbdb218e6372e","tid":1939030,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"二戰都取消過, 而家個局勢仲嚴峻過打仗都唔肯取消, 查實奧委會係咪收左回扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be9ec98927348963a9c78d1dd5ee412d3a0d096","tid":1939030,"uid":31098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"要其他奧委會出哂公開信先考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都好過唔聽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" 